id: monica-platform
title: "Make monica-cli secure, dependable, and agent-ready"
description: "Long-lived product program for a secure, maintained, well-tested Monica CRM CLI with durable project context."
type: Epic
status: open
priority: 0
tags[4]: agent-ux,product,reliability,security
created_at: "2026-07-16T16:56:16.513Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-16T17:20:57.557Z"
deadline: "2027-07-16T16:56:16.513Z"
assignee: codex-root
author: codex-root
estimated_minutes: 9600
acceptance_criteria: No open critical or high dependency vulnerabilities; supported dependencies and Actions stay current; required CI and security workflows pass; public commands remain documented and covered; tracker health remains valid
definition_of_ready: Repository baseline and GitHub state are inventoried; changes have acceptance tests and rollback-aware scope.
goal: trusted-monica-cli
objective: secure-maintainable-agent-cli
value: Reliable automation over personal CRM data
impact: Reduces security exposure and maintenance drag while preserving predictable agent workflows
outcome: A continuously healthy CLI with actionable project context and verified releases
why_now: A critical Vitest advisory and a backlog of failing Dependabot upgrades require immediate consolidation
reviewer: unbraind
risk: high
confidence: 90
sprint: 2026-07-security-modernization
release: next
comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:56:16.513Z",codex-root,"GitHub inventory on 2026-07-16 found no ordinary issues, 13 open dependency PRs, one critical Dependabot alert, no secret alerts, and only dismissed CodeQL alerts."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:56:16.513Z",codex-root,Authoritative tracker state is repository-local under .agents/pm and must only be changed through pm CLI.
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:56:16.513Z",codex-root,"All dependency PR failures appear to share a repository gate or compatibility surface, so updates should be integrated and verified as one coherent modernization tranche."
